Revision history for Perl extension Lingua::SV::Num2Word.

0.01	- original version;
        - number to text conversion for whole numbers from 0 up to 999 999 999

0.02	- changes for coding guideline compliance

0.03	- changed split to use negative param in split uses, makes code cleaner

0.04    - bug solved with numbers ending with 00, 000, etc.

